    {
      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-803a-8400-d1f0f7659956",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors use 5 assignments and one exam mark as predictors to overall scores of students. The novelty factors from their combination of Tree-Structured Parzen Estimation and SVR. Authors evaluate their approach against other models on a sample of 492 students taking a general science course. Models are also interpreted using LIME and SHapley. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-803a-8400-d1f0f7659956",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
