    {
      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-8097-a342-cda28412d0f1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Results show that their model outperforms all others used, achieving the lowest RMSE, RRMSE, highest Wilmott’s index, Legates-McGabe index (LM) and Nash-Sutcliffe Efficiency. LIME also shows that exam grade is the most important factor.",
